high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden table to the left of the couch.
Pick up the remote off of the shelf below the wooden table.
Put the remote in the cardboard box on the wooden table.
Pick up the cardboard box with the remote in it.
Walk over to the chair to the right of the couch.
Put the cardboard box with the remote in it on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a remote in it on the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Go to the wooden end table in front.
Pick up the remote on the bottom shelf of the end table.
Place the remote in the cardboard box on top of the end table.
Pick up the box with remote in it.
Turn right to go to the front of the white and gray arm chair on the opposite side.
Place the box with remote in it on the arm chair.
anns.task_desc: Move the box with remote in it from the end table to the arm chair.

high_descs: Take a step to the right and move forward to the table.
Pick up the remote from the bottom shelf of the table.
Place the remote in the box on the top right of the table.
Pick up the box from the top right of the table.
Take the box and turn to the right, then face the chair on the left across the room.
Place the box on the stripped chair.
anns.task_desc: Move a remote and box to a chair.
